data.description: Hop aboard the Sit-to-Stand Ultimate Alphabet Train by VTech! This train is designed to grow with your child and can be used for floor play or as a ride on that also transforms into a walker. Play ten activities while learning letters, numbers, colors and more.

data.title: Bead Maze Cube by KidKraft
data.description:
So many choices! Our Bead Maze Cube gives the young boys and girls in your life 5 sides of fun to choose from. Each side gives young kids a different activity that will help with the development of color recognition, shape recognition, and eye-hand coordination.
*Adorable farm theme, complete with tractors, trees, and a big farmhouse.
*Bead maze with pieces of solid wood.
*Tracking maze with six different pieces to move.
*Shape sorter
*Rotating gears
*Movable tiles with numbers on one side and colorful shapes on the other
*No assembly required.

Dimensions: 10.7"L x 10.5"W x 18.5"H
Materials: Wood
Country of Origin: China
